Information.LongDescription:
BRAND NEW apartments. SAVE up to 1.5 months FREE!*

Ask about our impressive penthouses with 10-foot ceilings, upgraded appliances, and custom closet systems!
Inspired choice. Modern living. Enjoy spacious floor plans, unparalleled amenities, and eco-friendly features at Sedona|Slate. All centered in a vibrant neighborhood just three blocks from the Rosslyn Metro. You’ll find a range of nightlife, cultural and outdoor activities waiting for you right outside your door.
Information.DrivingDirections: From I-66 East, take exit 73 to Lee Hwy/Rt 29. Turn R on N Fort Myer Dr. Turn R on Wilson Blvd. Turn L on N Pierce St. Turn L on Clarendon Blvd. The Leasing Office is located in Sedona on the lobby level.

Policy.General: Garage parking available. Please see Leasing Consultant for details.Woof! Meow! Pets up to 100 lbs are welcome.
